Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,室長…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 這裡交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 副室長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,室長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我記得…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是Scepter4中的重要人物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我有些話想跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒這樣做了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有點不太順手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是幻覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 請不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是調整了你的生物波動頻率
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後與我同步而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 讓你暫時成為我的氏族成員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在白銀聖域內與我共享重力平衡感
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放我下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打倒他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,體育場那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八…八田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.81,0:08:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 黑犬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.92,0:09:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通告兩族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻終止戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是第一王權者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.03,0:09:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白銀之王的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你睡糊塗了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說我的王只有赤之王 周防尊一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰理他什麽白銀之王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,領導Scepter4的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也只有青之王 宗像禮司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有義務遵從其他王的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我問你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們真的明白兩王的真意何在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赤之王…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,周防尊為何要佔領學園島？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,青之王…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宗像禮司為何不親自指揮？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有兩人為何不加入己陣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而要獨自做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:10:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們的王也許命令你們戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是狀況不斷變化著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該放下武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待王的下一個命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,區區野狗說什麼蠢話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別來礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很不爽但猴子說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.65,0:10:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙更不值得信任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來就沒想只靠勸說就能解決
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草薙哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑犬在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.10,0:10:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑犬在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說那影像裡的小鬼也在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:10:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你們怎麼會來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我有事要找你們商量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次又怎麽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許是打給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們誰能接一下電話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是周防尊的參謀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草薙出雲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你那邊應該有個嬉皮笑臉的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他聽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問您是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國常路大覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黃金之王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.05,0:13:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才剛開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始可不能喊停了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你停的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有停過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.07,0:13:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:13:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太安靜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.54,0:14:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是變得越來越詭異了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是我要說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又給中尉添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是這麼想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那至少盡點王應當履行的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是過分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我現在才會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的狀況有一半是你自作自受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算變成老爺爺了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中尉還是中尉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連愛說教這點也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麽解決？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確很像你的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還想說時隔半個世紀終於回地上了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.72,0:15:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真想再見一次面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你既然這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就別這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正說了你也不會聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.34,0:15:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真明白我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這次又得說再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:23.82,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2}請多保重 我的老友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:27.83,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2}\N做得漂亮點 威斯曼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白銀之王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我伊佐那社就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麽 伊佐那社
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依照你的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先已確保了學生們的撤離路線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在正由我們所指揮的兩族成員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始引導學生們撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.01,0:15:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你說的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無色之王也有可能轉換到學生身上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁機逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 他的目標是王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以為此引來赤之王和青之王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此學生們反而應儘快離開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是無色之王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你們逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃也是沒有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.40,0:16:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被擺弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被擺弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直到死都被我擺弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我的手中 毀滅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}那聲音在頭裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把一切都交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無色之王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}經驗 能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\pos(324,427)}所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 本來大家都處於不安的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.41,0:17:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是比之前更強的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎麽做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我至今為止…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有自己的氏族成員
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為我第一個夥伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白是貓的小白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓早就是小白的貓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.53,0:17:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經…已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經顧不上我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要逃的話就趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麽逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要死在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.71,0:18:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要放棄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.40,0:18:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那影像裡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 都是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們才…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.73,0:18:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像在哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在立刻離開學園島
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再讓你們受到傷害了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不認識你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然大家都不認識我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我認識你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.17,0:19:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我會引導大家離開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請相信我跟著我走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威斯曼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許對其他人出手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.71,0:19:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們來做個了斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.17,0:20:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吾輩…做到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是白銀之…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都平安離開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.82,0:20:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩位 感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.17,0:20:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白銀之王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無法做任何的承諾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.61,0:21:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡我所能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:28.92,Default1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a2}祝你們好運
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做個了斷？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是沒用的掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赤和青
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要把這兩個王控制到手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後就是照我說的算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.78,0:22:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 真的能控制得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.06,0:22:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我

